Body: Thank you for all the support.  Many of you are asking for the contract address to be published. Since contributions are not allowed at this time (because the token swap event is not yet started), we don't want people to send ether to the contract and have their transaction fail. That's why we will publish the contract address concurrently with the launch of the token swap event.  The total amount of tokens in circulation will be determined at the end of the token swap event. No more tokens will ever be created after the token swap is completed.

Author: noonedime
Title: [ANN]: The Number One Dime token swap event
Body: The Number One Dime Token swap event done  https://i.imgur.com/UUBJmv4.png  https://number1dime.org Twitter: https://twitter.com/TheNumber1Dime  The Number One Dime is inspired by the first coin that Scrooge McDuck had ever earned. For more information check our website at https://number1dime.org  Token Information ERC20 standard ethereum based token Name: Number One Dime Symbol: N1D Decimals: 0 Contract address:  0x3c22ae85b4ee099f4fd656872343c95ff74d57d4 https://etherscan.io/token/0x3c22ae85b4ee099f4fd656872343c95ff74d57d4  Token Swap Event done Start: 2017-11-13 End: 2017-12-31  Value Proposition This is a collector token issued in exchange for the lowest possible amount of ether: 1 wei. The token is already deployed on the ethereum blockchain. The contract source code is published and verified so it's fully transparent. It is a token that could be nice to have in anyone's portfolio, but it also brings a very high upside potential. If traded for ether on exchanges, the lowest possible bid price will be 1 wei, it can't be lower than that. 100% of tokens will be distributed during the token swap event. No presale, no discounts, no bounty programs. Everyone gets the tokens on the same terms.  White Paper download from the website https://number1dime.org  Exchanges https://etherdelta.com/#0x3c22ae85b4ee099f4fd656872343c95ff74d57d4-ETH
